quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"In the name of Allah, the Entirely Merciful, the Especially Merciful"
  1,2,"All praise belongs to Allah, the Lord of the universe"
  1,3,"The most Merciful, the most Beneficent"
  1,4,Master of the Day of Judgment
  1,5,"You alone do we worship, and You alone do we ask for help"
  1,6,Guide us to the Straight Path
  1,7,"The path of those upon whom You have bestowed Your blessings! Not the path of those who earned Your wrath, or erred and went astray"
